    "There are lots of neurons in each layer, and each neuron in the current layer is connected to all the neurons in the next layer, i.e., the full-connected structure.",
    "Specifically, every neuron performs the affine transform on the input followed by the non-linear activation function to achieve the non-linear mapping.",
